An approach to data cleaning

What we talk about when we talk about data

We need to think about what we do when we do data cleaning. We're going to follow a simple procedure:

  1. Looking at the data
  2. Thinking about "what is this data good for" – what will you make with it
  3. thinking about the steps needed to transform one into another (pseudocode)
  4. exploring the tidyverse
